These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daffodil
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, golf
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Transport      | quad-bike     | bike |
| Flower   | daffodil | bellflower      |
| Sport         | golf    | biathlon      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, singing
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, freelancer
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, lime
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the project-manager##1
2. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |
| Hobby         | singing      | magic-tricks |
| Job   | freelancer | project-manager    |
| Food           | lime         | eggplant         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-3::.
City: colone, london
2 different pets are kept: mouse, pony
2 different games are played: bridge, chess
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |
| City         | colone | london |
| Pet         | pony       | mouse       |
| Game   | chess       | bridge         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-4::.
