.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, zombie
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, magic-tricks
City: marseilles, liverpool
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | zombie   |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks          | baking   |
| City         | marseilles     | liverpool |

 